OL,5, A motorist fined after driving through 
OL,6, Gatwick Airport's drop-off zone        
OL,7, successfully challenged it using an    
OL,8, artificial intelligence (AI) chatbot.  
OL,10,FShaun Bosley, from Brighton, dropped a 
OL,11,Fwork colleague at the airport in       
OL,12,FNovember and received a #100 "final    
OL,13,Fnotice" from NCP several months later. 
OL,15,FHe turned to AI, using ChatGPT to      
OL,16,Fgenerate a human-like appeal, saying he
OL,17,Fhad had no previous notice of the fine.
OL,19,FMr Bosley said NCP reduced the fine to 
OL,20,F#15, which was the original amount.    
